snippet.title: Vampire Survivors - Launch Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Vampire Survivors is available now on Nintendo Switch: https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/vampire-survivors-switch/ 

Mow down thousands of night creatures and survive until dawn! With nowhere to run or hide, all you can do is survive against massive hordes of monsters. Vampire Survivors is a gothic horror casual game with rogue-lite elements, where your choices can allow you to quickly snowball against the hundreds of monsters that get thrown at you. 

#VampireSurvivors #NintendoSwitch
